          <vesection name="body">--><div class="details_wrapper newsroom_details_wrapper"><div class="details_page_title"><h1>News</h1></div><div class="details_content_wrapper news_content_wrapper"><div class="layout_2cols_nw"><div class="layout_2cols_w details_content"><div class="news_header"><div class="news_date_subtype"><span class="news_details_date">June 14, 2004</span><span class="news_details_sub_type">Press Release</span></div><h2 class='news_name'>Twelve Associates Elected to the Michael Best & Friedrich LLP Partnership</h2></div><div class="news_desc"><p>Milwaukee, WI - Michael Best &amp; Friedrich LLP is pleased to announce the following associates who have been elected to the firm's partnership:</p>
